text: Where No Vultures Fly is a 1951 British adventure movie directed by Harry Watt and starring Anthony Steel, Dinah Sheridan, Harold Warrender, William Simons. It was followed up by the 1954 sequel West of Zanzibar. ==Other websites== * * Category:1951 adventure movies Category:British adventure movies Category:Movies directed by Henry Watt
title: Where No Vultures Fly
